    "content": {
        "rendered": "<h2>Basic Setup</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Create a new Field Group</li>\n<li>Add a Button Group field</li>\n<li>Configure the choices:\n<ul>\n<li>Add value:label pairs</li>\n<li>Set a default value</li>\n<li>Choose return format</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Common Use Cases</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Simple Toggle Options\n<ul>\n<li>Yes/No choices</li>\n<li>Show/Hide settings</li>\n<li>Layout selections</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Status Selection\n<ul>\n<li>Draft/Review/Published</li>\n<li>Active/Inactive</li>\n<li>Priority levels</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Tips</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Keep choices concise</li>\n<li>Use clear labels</li>\n<li>Consider mobile usability</li>\n<li>Limit number of options</li>\n</ul>\n",
